article.headline: Tulane 78, Savannah State 60
article.story: NEW ORLEANS (AP) -- David Gomez scored 19 points to lead Tulane to a 78-60 win over Savannah State Saturday. Chris Moore added 13 points and Vytas Tatarunas had 12 for the Green Wave (4-8). Javon Randolph led Savannah State (1-16) with 18 points. Joseph Flegler added 16 and Michael Bennett finished with 10. Tulane led 46-21 at the half, and got 42 points from its bench. The Green Wave had their largest lead of the game with 32 seconds remainined in the first quarter when they were up by 25.
